parameters:
After finishing the committee work and stepping outside, the sky was
dyed a beautiful sunset hue, and the sun was on the verge of setting.

Flora: "Maybe I pushed myself a little too hard... Let's head home
quickly!"
Flora: "What? What was that just now...?"

\N[301]: "Kukukuku... Traveling through time and space sure is
exhausting~"

Suddenly, a monster like nothing she'd ever seen before appeared
before her, grinning hideously.

\N[301]: "Kekkekeke... So this is the so-called Warrior of Light? Hmm~
I can sense the power of light, but it's not very strong."
\N[301]: "Hmm~? Has this one yet to realize her own power? Kekkeke~"
「それにしても、\SE[KO_Gokuri01,90,100,0]\N[301]: "Gulp... It's a shame to dispose of such a beautiful girl."

\N[301]: "It's true~ Just looking at this young lady made this get
all~ excited."

Twitching, twitching... The monsters thrust their hips forward,
showing off their grotesque penises twitching.
Flora: (Wh-What are these people?! Who are they exactly?!)

Shaking, shaking, shaking... Frozen with fear, she couldn't move her
body to escape...

\N[301]: "To think such a one is the Warrior of Light, curse your
fate..."

Flora crouched down on the spot, clutching her head... Faces of her
kind parents and friends flashed through her mind.
Lize: "It seems I made it just in time..."
Lize: "I am Lize... Leave this to me."

\N[301]: "Oh, you're the Priestess of Light... Damn it! Do it, finish
her off!"

The girl who called herself Lize easily dodged the attacks with her
rod.

\N[301]: "What kind of person is this... But I won't be taken down so
easily!"

Lize: (Damn, no good... The teleportation has drained my magic
power...)
Flora tightly grasped the hand of the girl who called herself Lize.
Lize: "No, not like that... Hold it like this."
The two held hands in a lovers' grip... Squeeze♪

Thump thump thump thump... Flora's power of light flowed into Lize's
body.
\N[301]: "Damn it~! You guys! Stop flirting around~! Take this~!!!"

\N[301]: "Damn it, I was going to use this on the Warrior of Light,
but I'll give it to you instead!!!"
The monster threw a scroll emitting black light into the air!

\N[301]: "It's a curse of ability reduction! Hahaha, now you too will
be... guh, gaaaahhh~!!!"
The exhausted monster shattered while screaming!
Lize: "*pant* *pant*... It looks like it's finally over."
Flora: "My name is Flora. Thank you for saving me."

Lize: "Let me introduce myself again, I am Lize... There's something
important I need to talk to you about."
Flora detailed everything that happened today to her parents.
